00:17:08.940 --> 00:17:11.230
-Pero...
- Es suficiente.

00:17:11.990 --> 00:17:13.950
Me gusta estar con Woo-hyeol.

00:17:14.030 --> 00:17:15.160
In-hae.

00:17:15.240 --> 00:17:17.370
